  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate the safety and efficacy of AeriSeal System
      treatment plus optimal medical therapy compared in patients with advanced upper lobe
      predominant (ULP) heterogeneous emphysema.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
